<element name="Shifter Arrow" type="Item" source="Player’s Handbook" id="ID_WOTC_PHB_ITEM_ARROW">
<description>
<p>This arrow has an arrowhead with 3 golden teardrops engraved in it with a slight glow to the gold.</p>
  <p class="indent">
    <strong>
      <em>Shift.</em>
    </strong>
    Whenever this arrow is fired, may choose to either have the arrow return to the one who fired it or create a spectral copy in its place as long as the original is no longer in the owners possession.
  </p>
</description>
<setters>
<set name="category">Homebrew Ammunition</set>
<set name="cost" currency="cp">0</set>
<set name="weight" lb="0.05">1/20 lb.</set>
<set name="type">Ammunition</set>
<set name="Ammunition">SAMPLE Arrow</set>
<set name="stackable">true</set>
</setters>
</element>
	<element name="SAMPLE Arrow" type="Item" source="Player’s Handbook" id="ID_WOTC_PHB_ITEM_SAMPLE_ARROW">
